---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "PawPicks UK — Honest Pet Product Reviews"
description: "Independent UK pet product reviews. Grain-free dog food, harnesses, beds and more. Real recommendations from real dog owners, backed by data."
---

{% block hero %}
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Honest Pet Product Reviews</h1>
    <p>Independent, data-driven recommendations from real UK dog owners. No sponsorships. No fluff. Just the best products for your dog.</p>
  </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<h2 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🏆 Top-Rated Grain-Free Dog Foods (March 2026)</h2>
<p style="color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">We've tested and compared the most popular grain-free dog foods available in the UK. Here are our top picks.</p>

<div class="product-grid">
  {% for product in products.grainFreeDryFood | sortByRating | limit(4) %}
  <div class="product-card">
    {% if loop.index == 1 %}<span class="badge badge--top">🏆 Top Pick</span>{% endif %}
    {% if product.bestValue %}<span class="badge badge--value">💰 Best Value</span>{% endif %}
    <h3><a href="/best-grain-free-dog-food-uk/#{{ product.slug }}">{{ product.name }}</a></h3>
    <div class="rating">{{ product.rating | stars }} ({{ product.rating }}/5)</div>
    <p class="meta">{{ product.brand }} · {{ product.weight }} · {{ product.meatContent }} meat</p>
    <p>{{ product.summary | truncate(120) }}</p>
    <div class="price">{{ product.price | gbp }} <span style="font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-text-light);">({{ product.pricePerKg | gbp }}/kg)</span></div>
    <a href="/best-grain-free-dog-food-uk/#{{ product.slug }}" class="cta">Read Full Review →</a>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 2rem 0;">
  <a href="/best-grain-free-dog-food-uk/" class="cta" style="display: inline-block; background: var(--color-primary); color: #fff; padding: 0.8rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem;">See All 8 Grain-Free Dog Foods Compared →</a>
</div>

<h2 style="margin-top: 3rem;">Why Trust PawPicks?</h2>
<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin: 1.5rem 0;">
  <div style="padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--color-bg-alt); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
    <h3>🐕 Real Dog Owners</h3>
    <p>We own a grain-sensitive Labrador/Lurcher. We don't just review products — we live with the consequences of bad food choices.</p>
  </div>
  <div style="padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--color-bg-alt); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
    <h3>📊 Data-Driven</h3>
    <p>Every review includes protein %, meat content, price per kg, and ingredient analysis. Numbers don't lie — marketing does.</p>
  </div>
  <div style="padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--color-bg-alt); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
    <h3>🚫 Never Sponsored</h3>
    <p>We may earn affiliate commissions, but we never accept free products or payments for reviews. Our picks are genuinely our picks.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 style="margin-top: 3rem;">🐕 Breed-Specific Food Guides</h2>
<p style="color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Every breed has different nutritional needs. Find the best grain-free food for your dog.</p>
<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
  <a href="{{ '/best-dog-food-for-labradors/' | url }}" style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--color-bg-alt); border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
    <strong>🦮 Labradors</strong><br><span style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-light);">Joint support + weight management</span>
  </a>
  {% for breed in breeds %}
  <a href="{{ ('/best-dog-food-for-' + breed.slug + '/') | url }}" style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--color-bg-alt); border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
    <strong>🐾 {{ breed.name }}s</strong><br><span style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-light);">{{ breed.commonHealthIssues[0] | capitalize }} + {{ breed.commonHealthIssues[1] }}</span>
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<h2 style="margin-top: 3rem;">Popular Guides</h2>
<ul style="line-height: 2;">
  <li><a href="{{ '/best-grain-free-dog-food-uk/' | url }}">Best Grain-Free Dog Food UK (2026) — Full Comparison</a></li>
  <li><a href="{{ '/is-grain-free-dog-food-good/' | url }}">Is Grain-Free Dog Food Actually Good for Dogs?</a></li>
  <li><a href="{{ '/grain-free-vs-regular-dog-food/' | url }}">Grain-Free vs Regular Dog Food — What's the Difference?</a></li>
  <li><a href="{{ '/best-dog-food-for-labradors/' | url }}">Best Dog Food for Labradors (2026 Guide)</a></li>
</ul>
{% endblock %}
